---
<div class="about-us-area">
    <div class="content">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="container-area">
                <div class="content-area">
                    <h4>About Us</h4>
                    <h3 class="heading">Let us takecare of all your cleaning service needs.</h3>
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. 
